{"tid":1494770,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"毛澤東: 〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T06:17:08.000Z","uid":57076,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e91af509f3c304321623ee5628c71fd1ae19ef20","tid":1494770,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:54:05.000Z","msg":"「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」[10]<br />\n<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家記住，當中國強烈譴責香港人，話係暴徒，林鄭班子指責暴力示威，大家就知道我地做啱了<br />\n<br />\n但當香港政府同三毛都讚揚818和平示威，大家就要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然我認為係機場等場面大家都需要做和理非，但係各區示威，勇武都需要做和理非既盾，好似元朗勇武手足咁保護和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4097cca144412926d34d01843b41e217ed93cadb","tid":1494770,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb178b2545018da7f80cb91731085319d51d095","tid":1494770,"uid":29153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:03:22.000Z","msg":"用老共思維反老共<br />\n毛主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf77fc1feb0d3bdf6f33919c968157d62ab37f9c","tid":1494770,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:04:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bf39dfbea2ca1c4929391f756f12e27fabc0d23","tid":1494770,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:04:52.000Z","msg":"林鄭話社會變平靜個下就要知勇武要進場"},{"pid":"899280acc60cee4555da2266a2f5c2d3a3894c2a","tid":1494770,"uid":126632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:06:01.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148590c75de89825bf25b737c11c2408b90e9fae","tid":1494770,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:08:42.000Z","msg":"所謂「打著紅旗反紅旗」並唔係指舉支那旗黎示威咁撚膚淺<br />\n而係利用毛魔嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">思想理念</span>去打返而家嘅共產黨"},{"pid":"6fa77b6f4241b418abeb98e3daf4a359b2e8dff1","tid":1494770,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"148590c75de89825bf25b737c11c2408b90e9fae","tid":1494770,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:08:42.000Z","msg":"所謂「打著紅旗反紅旗」並唔係指舉支那旗黎示威咁撚膚淺<br />\n而係利用毛魔嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">思想理念</span>去打返而家嘅共產黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:11:47.000Z","msg":"學習毛澤東革命思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以灌輸埋比藍絲"},{"pid":"2803de402dfac94cf3e8feb85888c3cea0ebe1dd","tid":1494770,"uid":149566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4FirZU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4FirZU.png&h=342929a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53fKnyh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53fKnyh.png&h=1fc3bafe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#Eye4HK<br />\n#EyeforHK<br />\n#NoPoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK<br />\n#CondemnHKpolicebrutality<br />\n#LiberateHK<br />\n#WeareHongKonger"},{"pid":"400b4e0103793bcc1185ca185e90acd1a0897d3e","tid":1494770,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2803de402dfac94cf3e8feb85888c3cea0ebe1dd","tid":1494770,"uid":149566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4FirZU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4FirZU.png&h=342929a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53fKnyh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt